Act 2002 is your main tool.

00:04:46.775 --> 00:04:50.885
It provides the legal muscle for
banks to recover bad loans, which

00:04:50.885 --> 00:04:55.505
directly impacts the bank's health
and asset quality, and everyone.

00:04:55.965 --> 00:04:56.895
Absolutely.

00:04:56.895 --> 00:05:02.055
Everyone in a bank must be aware of the
prevention of money laundering Act 2002.

