key terms specific to each act, like what

00:07:10.810 --> 00:07:16.150
exactly counts as a negotiable instrument
or money laundering or a secured creditor.

00:07:16.645 --> 00:07:19.255
Also know your regulatory authority.

00:07:19.555 --> 00:07:24.625
You must know which authority, like the
RBI is in charge of enforcing each act.

00:07:24.985 --> 00:07:29.455
Sometimes just knowing the chronological
order of these important acts

00:07:29.455 --> 00:07:33.685
can be a lifesaver, helping you
eliminate wrong options in a pinch.

