00:09:54.975 --> 00:09:57.464
Common mistakes and misconceptions.

00:09:57.855 --> 00:10:00.555
Be careful to avoid some common traps.

00:10:00.735 --> 00:10:05.985
A very frequent one is confusing years,
like mixing up the enactment years.

00:10:06.074 --> 00:10:11.594
For example, thinking PMLA is from
1999 when that's actually fe year.

00:10:12.510 --> 00:10:15.960
