instead of just foreign exchange.

00:10:21.060 --> 00:10:24.210
Don't fall into the trap
of overlooking amendments.

00:10:24.480 --> 00:10:29.220
A recent change might be what the
question is about, not the original text.

00:10:29.550 --> 00:10:34.350
Be cautious with interchangeable terms
as a word in one act might have a

00:10:34.615 --> 00:10:35.635
slightly different meaning in another.

